<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qcamerainfocontrol.xml">QCameraInfoControl</db:link> class provides information about the camera devices available on the system.</db:para>
<db:para>The interface name of <db:link xlink:href="qcamerainfocontrol.xml">QCameraInfoControl</db:link> is <db:code>org.qt-project.qt.camerainfocontrol/5.3</db:code> as defined in <db:link xlink:href="qvideodeviceselectorcontrol.xml#QCameraInfoControl_iid">QCameraInfoControl_iid</db:link>.</db:para>
</db:section>
